Install sass & compass:

gem install sass
gem install compass

Compile scss to css:

# sass --watch public/css/sass:public/css/gen

DEV:

compass watch .
nodemon app.js (or better to automatically add missing envs: ./start-server)

Add missing env variables: source envs

Install r.js in /build

node build/r.js -o build/build-profile.js

SUBLIME:

"folder_exclude_patterns": [".sass-cache"]